OL,3,CSpecialist unit transforming care for
OL,4,Colder people
OL,6,FA specialist unit aimed at getting
OL,7,Folder people in and out of hospital
OL,8,Fand back into their homes as quickly
OL,9,Fas possible has been created.
OL,11,FThe frailty clinic, at Manchester
OL,12,FRoyal Infirmary A&E, offers advice,
OL,13,Fguidance, investigations, treatment
OL,14,Fand onward referrals if needed.
OL,16,FIt means older people can get back to
OL,17,Ftheir normal lives as quickly as
OL,18,Fpossible with the best specialist care
OL,19,Favailable, and without the need for
OL,20,Flong stays in hospital.
