OL,3,CSpecialist unit transforming care for
OL,4,Colder people
OL,6,FThe team behind it believe this in
OL,7,Fturn will also improve their health
OL,8,Fand helps out supporting family
OL,9,Fmembers and carers massively.
OL,11,FThe unit, which opened in October, has
OL,12,Fso far seen more than 1,000 patients -
OL,13,Fwith 70% discharged the same day.
OL,15,FThe freed up capacity means the main
OL,16,FA&E department can see other patients
OL,17,Fquicker and more effectively.
