OL,6,FGwenda Watson, 93, was out of hospital
OL,7,Fin less than a week after suffering a
OL,8,Ffall, much to her and her family's
OL,9,Frelief.
OL,11,F"Their routine isn't always yours,"
OL,12,FGwenda said, "but you try and
OL,13,Faccommodate it, and get on with it,
OL,14,Fhoping to get home sooner."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
