OL,4,Colder people
OL,6,FHer daughter, Megan Marsh said: "Being
OL,7,Fin hospital I could really see the
OL,8,Fdecline in terms of mobility, just
OL,9,Fbeing bewildered about what was going
OL,10,Fon there, and we had a team from the
OL,11,FHospital at Home service, who came to
OL,12,Fsee mum at the hospital and made
OL,13,Farrangements for her to come back to
OL,14,Fher house.
OL,16,F"That was one of the best things, it
OL,17,Fmeant that she didn't have to stay in
OL,18,Fhospital for any longer than she
OL,19,Fneeded to in that environment to get
OL,20,Fback to her own surroundings."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
