OL,4,Colder people
OL,6,FDr Scott Mather, a Consultant
OL,7,FPhysician and Geriatrician, said the
OL,8,Fpragmatic approach helps reduce time
OL,9,Fin hospital as those seen by medics
OL,10,Fwho are not experts in looking after
OL,11,Folder people increases the risk of
OL,12,Fspending a longer time there.
OL,14,F"It's not just doctors and nurses on
OL,15,Fthe ward," he said. "It's pharmacists
OL,16,Fand therapists and a whole range of
OL,17,Fdifferent professionals.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
