OL,3,CSpecialist unit transforming care for
OL,4,Colder people
OL,6,F"We're trying to assess our patients
OL,7,Fin a much more pragmatic and holistic
OL,8,Fway and also to reduce the amount of
OL,9,Ftime people spend in the emergency
OL,10,Fdepartment."
OL,12,FDawn Gudegast, a senior
OL,13,Fphysiotherapist added: "Assessing
OL,14,Fpatients in this environment and as
OL,15,Fquickly as possible we stop any
OL,16,Fdecline in their cognitive function.
OL,18,F"They are not disorientated. They get
OL,19,Fhome quicker... and we stop any muscle
OL,20,Fwastage or change in the patient."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
