OL,3,CSpecialist unit transforming care for
OL,4,Colder people
OL,6,FThe ward also helps some people get
OL,7,Fdischarged the same day, an important
OL,8,Ftask when those over 65 account for
OL,9,F40% of hospital admissions and occupy
OL,10,Faround two thirds of inpatient beds
OL,11,Fnationally.
OL,13,FSheila was one of the patients that
OL,14,Fwas in and out within the same day.
OL,16,FHer daughter Moira Maher said "They
OL,17,Fdid a brain scan, she had an X-ray,
OL,18,Fshe had all her bloods taken and we
OL,19,Fgot her medication and left at 4pm
OL,20,Fthat same day.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
