OL,6,F"She doesn't remember how ill she's
OL,7,Fbeen but she will remember someone
OL,8,Fspoke to her nicely, took her to the
OL,9,Ftoilet, and didn't make her feel like
OL,10,Fa burden because she needs help and
OL,11,Fshe's ringing the bell."
